{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_29","type":"agent_message","text":"Human intervention needed\n\nThe automated job failed for `org.apache.maven.resolver:maven-resolver-connector-basic:2.0.8`.\n\nPreserved work branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-5599-fails-java-run-org.apache.maven.resolver-maven-resolver-connector-basic-2.0.8-08bd5f9e\n\nThe first concrete failure was the JVM runtime `:test` / `:tckTest` stage. In `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.maven.resolver:maven-resolver-connector-basic:2.0.8/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-04T03-28-11-125783Z.log`, `Maven_resolver_connector_basicTest > connectorClosesTransporterAndRejectsFurtherTransfers()` fails because the test expects `repository().toString()`, but 2.0.8 returns `basic( central (https://repo.example.test/repository, default, releases+snapshots) )` from `connector.toString()`. The attempted automation in `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.maven.resolver:maven-resolver-connector-basic:2.0.8/fix-java-run-fail/pi-generation-2026-05-04T03-29-03-069623Z.log` updated that assertion to use `BasicRepositoryConnectorFactory.NAME + \"( \" + repository() + \" )\"`, but `stats/org.apache.maven.resolver/maven-resolver-connector-basic/2.0.8/execution-metrics.json` still reports overall failure with no final artifact (`generated_loc: 0`, `test_file: None`, `metadata_file: None`), so dynamic-access coverage was not produced.\n\nThere are also follow-on failures worth checking before landing a manual fix. `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.maven.resolver:maven-resolver-connector-basic:2.0.8/populate-artifact-urls/populate_artifact_urls.log` shows `:checkMetadataFiles` failing because `metadata/org.apache.maven.resolver/maven-resolver-connector-basic/2.0.8/reachability-metadata.json` is missing. After the tentative test fix, native trace verification surfaced metadata gaps: `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.maven.resolver:maven-resolver-connector-basic:2.0.8/native-test-verify/cycle-0-runNativeTraceImage-2026-05-04T03-29-41-806517Z.log` reports missing resource registration for `META-INF/services/org.slf4j.spi.SLF4JServiceProvider`, and `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.maven.resolver:maven-resolver-connector-basic:2.0.8/native-test-verify/cycle-1-runNativeTraceImage-2026-05-04T03-30-23-604241Z.log` reports missing reflection registration for `org.opentest4j.AssertionFailedError`.\n\n1. Apply the `connector.toString()` assertion update in `tests/src/org.apache.maven.resolver/maven-resolver-connector-basic/2.0.8/.../Maven_resolver_connector_basicTest.java` and rerun the `javaTest`/`test` lane for `org.apache.maven.resolver:maven-resolver-connector-basic:2.0.8`.\n2. Add or restore `metadata/org.apache.maven.resolver/maven-resolver-connector-basic/2.0.8/reachability-metadata.json`, then rerun `checkMetadataFiles`.\n3. If the Java lane passes, address the native-image metadata gaps from the two `native-test-verify` logs and regenerate stats so coverage can be evaluated."}}
